transcript_text: First Protein Theons 2-12, If I Bay ends up breaking thy heart, it is best to hit the gym rather than coping and tearing thyself apart.  Work out, sweat, and channel light emotion for the only worthwhile revenge is having me glow up for their lack of devotion.
